{"type": "article", "id": 26071, "title": "Coach 大规模重组，以及，“中指猫”春夏系列不错｜浮华日报", "description": "我们为你挑选了今天最重要和最好看的时尚新闻。", "date": "2016-04-27T10:52:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [{"id": 8698, "name": "重组"}, {"id": 26824, "name": "管理层"}, {"id": 1743, "name": "裁员"}, {"id": 2866, "name": "退休"}, {"id": 1618, "name": "赞助"}, {"id": 26825, "name": "夏日特辑"}, {"id": 5729, "name": "度假"}, {"id": 1782, "name": "Coach"}, {"id": 27, "name": "Nike"}, {"id": 3530, "name": "Forever 21"}, {"id": 2034, "name": "Dior"}, {"id": 7776, "name": "NikeLab"}, {"id": 4221, "name": "WSJ"}, {"id": 1508, "name": "Net-a-porter"}, {"id": 5228, "name": "UGG"}, {"id": 26826, "name": "Deckers"}], "category": 19, "column": 8, "author": 113313, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 54, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702150415snGYqu5JUeMNWCdB.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<h2>一些重要的新闻：</h2>\n<p><a href=\"http://www.mr-mag.com/andrea-odonnell-named-deckers-brands-president-fashion-lifestyle/\"><b>UGG 母公司任命新时尚生活方式总裁</b></a>｜UGG 母公司 Deckers Brand，旗下包括鞋履、服装和配饰等品牌，近日任命 Andrea O’Donnell  为时尚生活方式总裁，此前她是 DFS 集团全球经营部门总裁，连卡佛执行理事。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/eye/parties/san-francisco-2016-international-film-festival-gala-awards-mira-nair-jordana-brewster-olivia-culpo-10418595/\"><b>Net-a-porter 赞助旧金山国际电影节</b></a>｜奢侈品电商 Net-a-porter 在梅森堡（Fort Mason）为旧金山国际电影节联合主办晚宴及颁奖典礼，这是 Net-a-porter 第二次赞助这一活动。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/phil-knight-steps-down-nike-chairman\"><b>Nike 联合创始人将于六月隐退</b></a>｜去年我们报道过 Nike 联合创始人 Phil Knight 今年退休，近日在 CBS 最新的采访中 Phil Knight 表示将于六月正式从董事长职位离职，现任 Nike CEO Mark Parker 将接任董事长职位，品牌总裁 Trevor Edwards  任 CEO。同时 Phil Knight  的回忆录 <i>SHOE DOG</i> 也于今天正式发售。</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://wwd.com/accessories-news/financial/management-shakeup-coach-even-overseas-markets-boost-q3-results-handbags-shoes-accessories-fashion-human-resources-10418444/\"><b>Coach 管理层重组，裁员 300 人</b></a>｜Coach 最新公布了重组计划，包括裁去两名高级管理层和 300 个其它职位，为了达到 2017 年财年 20% 的营业利润率目标。品牌表示这样的变化有助于形成“敏捷且可伸缩的商业模式”，Andre Cohen 升至北美及全球市场部门总裁，Todd Kahn  升至总裁、首席行政官员及秘书，监管范围扩张至信息技术、供应链、全球环境及采购，Diane Mahady 总管全球经销。同时首席运营官兼总裁 Gebhard F. Rainer，全球营销、数字及消费者体验部门总裁 David Duplantis 离开公司。</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><a href=\"http://sg.fashionmag.com/news/Sales-in-China-Europe-drive-handbag-maker-Coach-s-profit,686380.html#.Vx_Pv4QrJQY\"><b>Coach 三年来首次季度利润增长</b></a>｜因中国、日本及欧洲地区表现良好，Coach 集团发布财报显示连续两个季度获得销售额增长，同时季度利润三年来首次增长。最大的市场北美地区的销售额上涨了 1% ，中国地区则有 2% 的涨幅。总收入上涨了 11.2% 至 10.3 亿美元，略胜于预期的 10.2 亿。</p>\n<h2>一些值得一看的：</h2>\n<p>洛杉矶的“中指猫”品牌 <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/ripndip-2016-spring-summer-collection\">RIPNDIP 2016 春夏系列</a>：</p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150353rvIpA8ZQoFEOV2mf.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150354AiaTvFyLqXjhCKNs.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021503552EGxO4qiIp8HQSoc.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150355SUGptIszfYZJxHi8.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/2016070215035695cF3VGBURJo2TjN.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150356GkiqsjuN8b7RnXZ0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150357N9WlzPipdghrVRQ1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150357zlob7POv8XiMp3hB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021503582Da1AwhKXfBPVtOE.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n<p><a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/nikelab-transform-jacket\">NikeLab 最新推出一种 Transform 夹克</a>，应对不同天气。包含一件御寒的抓绒夹克，其后背的拉链打开可以拿出一件超轻薄的防水梭织外套：</p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150359vcX6kaZY910E8FMK.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021504009VY6CdampyAE5gD1.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150400b70lLqkr1REpuPaI.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66666667\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"> <a href=\"http://hypebeast.com/2016/4/common-projects-chelsea-boot\">Common Projects 推出四色切尔西靴</a>：<br></p>\n<p class=\"multiple\"></p>\n<figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150401cVJtYnvmh6SeC0gB.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150401PhknoIcqB0Ov7F65.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66699219\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150402zgGbHZI4PMQWsBxX.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702150402OfVNGFePsB3A4QJL.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.66601562\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><p></p>\n<p class=\"\"><a href=\"http://www.fashiongonerogue.com/edita-vilkeviciute-vacation-style-wsj/\">超模 Edita Vilkeviciute 为华尔街日报<i> WSJ</i> 杂志四月刊拍摄大片</a>，开启度假模式：<br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<p></p>\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/201607021504034sgYEr